    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short story that turns everyday tasks into journeys. <i>Can you be the voice that doesn’t let her down?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intrusive Thoughts</strong> is a visual novel shown through an intense internal world. Simple actions like stepping outside or buying groceries become epic challenges for the protagonist, who is caught between biting humor and dark self-reflection. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each choice you make could lead to moments of surprising clarity or spiraling despair, as the main character's relentless inner voice shapes the way forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This isn’t just a story, it's an experience in mental and emotional landscapes. By being the first to understand her, maybe you’ll help her find a way through.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixelated graphic style</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short duration (20-30 minutes)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 different endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark immersive story</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
